Install requirements in txt file.

then type 

python3 -m flask run 

time to go localhost:5000/


Aim of the project
------------------
Read news,
tokenize it,
serve the sentences to the client to answer the sentence whether 1 or 0,
then create user selections to a new Folia XML Document

RTFM
----

Based on the news in

https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2018/1/1/archivelist/year-2018,month-1,starttime-43101.cms

For tokenizing the paragraphs, it's using python-ucto library.

https://github.com/proycon/python-ucto

For creating Folia document, it's using pynlpl library.

https://pynlpl.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
